high_descs: Turn right and walk around to face the couch side of the living room table.
Pick up the watch on the living room table.
Turn left and walk across the room to face the kitchen table.
Place the watch on the plate on the kitchen table.
Pick up the plate with a watch on it on the kitchen table.
Turn right and walk forward to face the living room table.
Place the plate with a watch on it on the living room table.
anns.task_desc: To put a watch on a plate plus move them to the living room table.

high_descs: Turn right.  Walk to the other side of the room.  Turn left at the couch.  Walk to the middle of the couch and turn left, facing the coffee table.
Pick up the watch on the coffee table.
Turn left and walk to the edge of the couch.  Turn right and walk to the other side of the room.  At the wall, turn right.  Walk to the kitchen table.
Put the watch down on the plate sitting on the kitchen table.
Pick up the plate with the watch on it.
Turn around.  Turn left toward the coffee table and turn left at the coffee table.
Sit the plate with the watch down on the coffee table at the nearest right corner, next to the box.
anns.task_desc: Put a watch on a plate and moved it to the coffee table.

high_descs: Take a step forward, then turn right and walk across the room, turn left before the red couch and walk over to the side of the coffee table.
Pick up the watch off of the coffee table.
Turn left and walk forward, hang a right after the coffee table and walk across the room, turn right before the wall and walk over to the round table.
Put the watch on the closest black and white plate on the table.
Pick up the plate with the watch on it off of the table.
Walk over to the closest side of the coffee table.
Put the black and white plate with the watch on it onto the front right corner of the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with a watch on it on the coffee table.
